=============
Pyrew
=============

Welcome to Pyrew, a Python library that provides a way to write shorter and more efficient Python code.

Installation
------------

1. Run the following command:

.. code-block:: bash

    pip install pyrew

2. At the top of your file, add the following code:

.. code-block:: python

    import pyrew

    pyrew = pyrew.Pyrew()
